{
  "stem": "945.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- they were strictly there for military purposes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Romanians, those that came back, some that had been in Vyshnivets before came back, and they took their vengeance out on the-- on the Yiddish population of Vyshnivets.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, the pain was pretty great in our family, having lost my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even to this day, it's very painful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We've lived with that pain all our lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But the worst was yet to come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know what was going to happen, how to organize our lives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Parents, of course, were concerned for the safety of their children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the whole community was very disturbed by what was going on, and very concerned about what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish school, of course, when the Soviet Union retreated, the Jewish school ceased to be a school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, personally was, while I was attending the Jewish school, they selected-- I don't remember-- three or five top students.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was amongst one of the top students that was to be sent to the Crimea as a prize for being a top student.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my papers were ready to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as it happened, the war started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the reason why I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- the-- as I explained before, the paradox in Russia was great.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because on the one hand, people-- people were starving, and people were scared, and people were ending up in jails, and people were being sent to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the other hand, they promoted theater, they promoted learning, they encouraged studies, they gave opportunities for people, especially for those that had the brains and the will to learn.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we now know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
